author: maxb
msg: Refactor the include structure of the SWIG bindings.
Tested to have no change to the generated wrappers (using SWIG 1.3.29).
* core.i: Move %inclusion of svn_*_h.swg here from svn_types.swg.
* include/apr.swg: Remove %inclusion of typemaps.i, which is already taken
Remove %inclusion of exception.i, as we are not using SWIG_exception().
Change %import of apr.swg to %include, add %include svn_string.swg.
Move %inclusion of svn_*_h.swg away to core.i.
* include/svn_string.swg: Remove %imports of apr.swg and svn_types.swg.
... and also update copyright and documentation comments.
